{"tid":968119,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新疆男童凍死河邊  網傳父母被捉入集中營","createTime":"2019-01-04T03:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T05:56:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7078090cfc88e5011665d4fff2b86a9d6b44c14e","tid":968119,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181229/large/1546071070_f4ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181229%2Flarge%2F1546071070_f4ce.jpg&h=8423e4b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新疆男童凍死在河邊。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在中共的鐵腕統治下，新疆大批民眾被關進「再教育營」洗腦。twitter流傳數張一名男童在河邊凍死的照片，據指這名男童的父母被關進「再教育營」，他在酷寒天氣下無法自食其力，最終在河邊活活凍死。<br />\n<br />\n一名名為Halmurat Harri Uyghur的twitter博客上傳了這些照片，他自稱是集中營受害人的兒子。他寫道這名男童的父母，來自新疆維吾爾自治區的和田地區墨玉縣巴西吉勒尕村，目前被關押在「再教育營」，年幼男童凍死在路邊，他指「即使人有不同的種族及宗教，都不應該有這樣的下場。」<br />\n<br />\ntwitter<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181229/59083435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181229%2F59083435&d=vzqZYnDb1ywAalcEFxHNhVzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=a02be9c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181229%2F59083435&h=cf34120f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181229/59083435</a>"},{"pid":"15237ce97325b7cc3d545eb11bc2d71b9644f705","tid":968119,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8febb7c8e29ad25ddba4abf10b25ae8af9a747","tid":968119,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"上次「敘利亞男孩」果班左膠呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw